Hello Matteo,

The UriUniqFilter of which BloomUriUniqFilter is an implementation is used
to prevent uris from being queued, processed and fetched repeatedly. If I&#39;m
not mistaken, if you were to exclude dns urls then they would be crawled
over and over again. So for good reason there&#39;s no facility for that in
heritrix.

Noah


